#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/gtk/GtkVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:20
#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/gtk/GtkVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:45
msgid ""
"Embeds a vtkRenderWindow into a pyGTK widget and uses "
"vtkGenericRenderWindowInteractor for the event handling.  This class embeds "
"the RenderWindow correctly.  A __getattr__ hook is provided that makes the "
"class behave like a vtkGenericRenderWindowInteractor."
msgstr ""

